Valentine's Day may have come and went but we are still in the mood for love as we discuss the latest entry in the Scott Pilgrim Universe! Join us as we strap in for a high-flying adventure into the world of Scott Pilgrim with our review of "Scott Pilgrim Takes Off." Released as a thrilling sequel to the cult classic "Scott Pilgrim vs. The World," this series takes us on a nostalgic journey through the beloved universe created by Bryan Lee O'Malley. With Michael Cera, Mary Elizabeth Winstead, and the ensemble breathe new life into their iconic roles, our hosts unpack the emotional rollercoaster that "Scott Pilgrim Takes Off" delivers, while speaking to the evolution of emotional maturity that permeates the entire series. Check it out now!Click on my link : [https://www.magicmind.com/MAJORISSUES](https://www.magicmind.com/areyouok) to enjoy up to 56% off your Magic Mind subscription and 20% on a one-time purchase with my code MAJORISSUES . Don't miss out on this limited-time offer!

  

